22
00:04:49,938 --> 00:04:53,374
Zato sam izostajala svo ovo vreme.

23
00:04:53,618 --> 00:04:55,529
Oni moraju da ga uklone.

24
00:04:55,578 --> 00:04:57,250
Ali je toliko veliki i opasan

25
00:04:57,298 --> 00:04:59,129
moraju da me operisu vise puta.

26
00:04:59,178 --> 00:05:02,170
Tako da sam preskocila celu proslu
skolsku godinu i ostala ovde do danas.

27
00:05:03,218 --> 00:05:05,937
Tako si mlada,i tako hrabra!

28
00:05:06,298 --> 00:05:08,334
Kada budes progledala,

29
00:05:08,538 --> 00:05:09,857
izvescu te negde da se igras.

30
00:05:09,898 --> 00:05:13,607
Svet je stvarno prelep.

31
00:05:21,538 --> 00:05:25,929
Wong Kar Mun, kada uklonim 
zavoje sa ociju.

32
00:05:26,138 --> 00:05:28,288
mozda ce te malo zaboleti.

33
00:05:28,338 --> 00:05:30,374
Ako mnogo boli ,recite mi odmah

34
00:05:30,418 --> 00:05:34,377
Ovo mozemo uraditi i sutra.

35
00:05:54,778 --> 00:05:57,417
Sada, pokusajte.

36
00:05:58,138 --> 00:06:02,097
Otvorite oci polako.

37
00:06:29,858 --> 00:06:32,372
Hej, nemojte se siliti ako
boli.

38
00:06:46,258 --> 00:06:49,694
Boli!

39
00:06:50,818 --> 00:06:53,127
Da li je previse bolno?

40
00:06:53,178 --> 00:06:55,817
Dr Lo, ona je sigrurno u velikim bolovima!

41
00:06:55,978 --> 00:06:59,368
Nikada nije plakala od bola
jos kada je bila dete!

42
00:06:59,578 --> 00:07:02,729
Bako, pustite Dr Lo da obavlja svoj posao.

43
00:07:04,578 --> 00:07:06,375
Nemojte se brinuti oko toga.

44
00:07:06,418 --> 00:07:08,454
Veoma malo pacijenata je imalo
odmah uspeha

45
00:07:08,498 --> 00:07:10,136
Potrebno je vreme...

46
00:07:10,178 --> 00:07:12,738
...za oci i glavu 
da se pronadju.

47
00:07:15,778 --> 00:07:18,736
Hajde!

48
00:07:51,538 --> 00:07:54,006
Jing Jing.

49
00:07:54,058 --> 00:07:57,289
Jing Jing.

50
00:08:01,378 --> 00:08:03,528
Zdravo, mozes li da vidis sad?

51
00:08:03,698 --> 00:08:06,815
Ja sam Jing Jing.

52
00:08:11,218 --> 00:08:13,857
Da li stvarno mozes da me vidis?

53
00:08:13,898 --> 00:08:16,970
Mislim da mogu videti. Nisam sigurna.

54
00:08:17,138 --> 00:08:19,129
Odlicno! Mozes da vidis!

55
00:08:19,178 --> 00:08:21,533
Sestro, moze da vidi!

56
00:08:22,098 --> 00:08:24,214
Sestro,

57
00:08:24,458 --> 00:08:25,527
njene oci rade!

58
00:08:25,578 --> 00:08:28,217
Moze da me vidi! Dodjite brzo!

59
00:08:56,138 --> 00:08:57,571
Bako!

60
00:08:57,618 --> 00:08:58,687
Bolnica zove!

61
00:08:58,738 --> 00:08:59,693
Molim?

62
00:08:59,738 --> 00:09:00,853
Mun moze da vidi!

63
00:09:00,898 --> 00:09:01,535
Stvarno?

64
00:09:01,578 --> 00:09:05,253
Idemo odmah u bolnicu!

65
00:09:05,298 --> 00:09:08,017
Hocete te li me otpustiti sada?

66
00:09:08,058 --> 00:09:09,286
Ne uskoro.

67
00:09:09,338 --> 00:09:11,408
Svaki primalac roznjace pocinje
da gleda kao kratkovid...

68
00:09:11,658 --> 00:09:13,694
za cak 1000 stepeni.

69
00:09:13,738 --> 00:09:16,298
Tek kada vasu ocni misici
budu u stanju da se prilagode,

70
00:09:16,538 --> 00:09:19,496
To ce pasti na 200 stepeni.

71
00:09:19,658 --> 00:09:21,774
Kada ce ona imati savrsen vid?

72
00:09:22,018 --> 00:09:23,292
Niko nema savrsen vid.

73
00:09:23,338 --> 00:09:25,329
Vecina ljudi su kratkog vida 
za oko 100 stepeni.

74
00:09:25,578 --> 00:09:27,296
Da li to znaci...

75
00:09:27,338 --> 00:09:29,135
...da ce morati da nosi naocare?

76
00:09:29,178 --> 00:09:30,327
To nece biti potrebno.

77
00:09:30,378 --> 00:09:33,575
Sve sto ona treba u ovom trenutku
su naocare za sunce.

78
00:09:34,458 --> 00:09:36,528
Mun, Odmori se malo.

79
00:09:36,578 --> 00:09:38,614
Ako sve bude islo po planu,
bice ranije otpustena.

80
00:09:45,698 --> 00:09:47,734
Mozes skinuti sada te
naocare za sunce.

81
00:09:48,018 --> 00:09:50,134
Pokusaj da se naviknes
na svetlo postepeno.

82
00:09:51,058 --> 00:09:52,332
Ako budes osecala bol,

83
00:09:52,378 --> 00:09:54,175
ili ako ti oci budu suzile,

84
00:09:54,218 --> 00:09:56,527
onda ces morati da zatvoris oci,

85
00:09:56,738 --> 00:09:58,057
i pustis oci da se odmore.

86
00:09:58,098 --> 00:09:59,531
Evo, ja cu vam pomoci oko kreveta.

87
00:09:59,578 --> 00:10:00,772
Sestro.

88
00:10:00,818 --> 00:10:02,968
Da li ima ogledalo 
u svakom toaletu?

89
00:10:03,338 --> 00:10:06,250
Ja cu vas odvesti tamo.

90
00:10:19,458 --> 00:10:22,495
Evo.

91
00:10:22,538 --> 00:10:25,735
Lagano.

92
00:10:26,218 --> 00:10:28,812
Uzmi svoje vreme i pozovi me
ako ti bude trebalo nesto.

93
00:12:00,018 --> 00:12:03,169
Ko je to?

94
00:12:06,138 --> 00:12:09,255
Jing Jing, jel si to ti?

95
00:12:09,298 --> 00:12:11,732
Zasto si toliko tiha?

96
00:12:11,778 --> 00:12:15,214
Imam jos jednu opreraciju
sutra.

97
00:12:15,538 --> 00:12:16,732
Obecala si da ces me izvesti
napolje kada progledas.

98
00:12:16,778 --> 00:12:18,131
Obelacala si mi da ces me izvesti...

99
00:12:18,178 --> 00:12:19,611
...kada budem progledala.

100
00:12:19,658 --> 00:12:21,091
Izacicemo napolje i zabaviti se...

101
00:12:21,138 --> 00:12:23,129
...posle tvoje operacije.

102
00:12:23,178 --> 00:12:25,373
Da li su ti rekli da mozes
vec sada napustiti bolnicu?

103
00:12:25,418 --> 00:12:26,897
Ne jos!

104
00:12:26,938 --> 00:12:29,577
Ali cak i ako mogu, moci cu uvek
da dodjem u posetu.

105
00:12:31,218 --> 00:12:33,891
Hajde da se slikamo zajedno.

106
00:12:34,138 --> 00:12:35,856
Hajdemo napolje! Hajde.

107
00:12:35,898 --> 00:12:38,128
Idemo... ali gde?

108
00:12:39,298 --> 00:12:41,528
Idemo ovuda!

109
00:12:41,698 --> 00:12:42,608
Sta je to?

110
00:12:42,658 --> 00:12:43,568
Kamera.

111
00:12:43,618 --> 00:12:44,892
Kamera?

112
00:12:44,938 --> 00:12:46,894
Sad, pogledaj ovamo.

113
00:12:46,938 --> 00:12:47,927
Ok.

114
00:12:47,978 --> 00:12:51,050
Spremna... 1, 2, 3!

115
00:14:57,418 --> 00:15:00,137
Madam, jel ste li dobro?

116
00:15:44,898 --> 00:15:47,048
Zdravo...

117
00:15:59,058 --> 00:16:02,289
<i>Smrzavam se...</i>

118
00:16:35,498 --> 00:16:37,568
Posaljite je u Blok-C.

119
00:16:37,618 --> 00:16:41,531
Blok-B nam je skroz popunjen.

120
00:17:04,858 --> 00:17:06,371
Sestro...

121
00:17:06,418 --> 00:17:08,568
da li je stara dama prosla ovuda?

122
00:17:10,098 --> 00:17:11,895
Da, Odveli smo je.

123
00:17:11,938 --> 00:17:13,690
Ali prosle noci...

124
00:17:13,738 --> 00:17:15,933
Videla sam nekog da joj je dosao u posetu.

125
00:17:16,138 --> 00:17:18,413
Cak su i izasli zajedno.

126
00:17:19,578 --> 00:17:21,057
Da li ste sigurni?

127
00:17:21,098 --> 00:17:24,977
Ne dopustamo posetu
nocu.

128
00:17:29,858 --> 00:17:31,337
Gde je Jing Jing?

129
00:17:31,378 --> 00:17:33,846
Otisla je na operaciju 
jutros.

130
00:17:50,458 --> 00:17:52,176
Dr. Lo je preporucio

131
00:17:52,218 --> 00:17:54,254
da ostanete jos dva dana...

132
00:17:54,298 --> 00:17:56,607
zato sto cu ja biti na poslovnom 
putovanju.

133
00:17:56,818 --> 00:17:58,888
Niko nece biti u 
mogucnosti da te pokupi.

134
00:17:59,658 --> 00:18:01,376
Lakse je bilo da te puste sada.

135
00:18:01,418 --> 00:18:02,612
Na ovaj nacin

136
00:18:02,658 --> 00:18:05,934
ti i baka mozete vise vremena
provesti zajedno.

137
00:18:06,498 --> 00:18:08,295
Moj... vec je 3 popodne!

138
00:18:08,338 --> 00:18:11,216
Nadam se da je ovo mesto lako naci...

139
00:18:27,898 --> 00:18:31,573
...nadamo se da nece biti kasno.

140
00:18:34,778 --> 00:18:38,657
Samo deset minuta kasnimo...
za nase imenovanje.

141
00:18:38,938 --> 00:18:42,010
Moracu otici zbog posla uskoro.

142
00:18:42,178 --> 00:18:44,328
Izvini.

143
00:18:44,378 --> 00:18:45,697
Dr. Lo je upravo izasao
na nekoliko minuta.

144
00:18:45,738 --> 00:18:46,614
Ok.

145
00:18:46,658 --> 00:18:47,613
Evo ga.

146
00:18:47,658 --> 00:18:48,932
Da li je 3 sata?

147
00:18:48,978 --> 00:18:50,536
Da, jeste.

148
00:18:50,578 --> 00:18:53,854
Mun, idemo.

149
00:18:54,578 --> 00:18:56,728
Dozvolite da vam predstavim
prirodu mog posla.

150
00:18:57,378 --> 00:18:59,130
Od sada,

151
00:18:59,178 --> 00:19:01,646
ja sam Wong Kar Mun's
psihoterapeut.

152
00:19:02,338 --> 00:19:05,171
Od kada je Gdjica. Wong izgubila vid
od svoje druge godine,

153
00:19:05,498 --> 00:19:07,807
njen vizuelni recnik

154
00:19:08,058 --> 00:19:09,491
je veoma ogranicen,

155
00:19:09,538 --> 00:19:12,098
i ona je najverovatnije zaboravila
veci deo njega.

156
00:19:12,818 --> 00:19:14,137
Da kazemo tako.

157
00:19:14,178 --> 00:19:16,169
Ms Wong, mozete li molim vas
skinuti naocare?

158
00:19:16,418 --> 00:19:18,693
I pustite da se vase oci 
naviknu na svetlost.

159
00:19:25,298 --> 00:19:29,052
Mozete li mi reci sta mi je u ruci?

160
00:19:36,298 --> 00:19:37,970
Shvaticete da je to 
heftalica...

161
00:19:38,018 --> 00:19:39,576
...kada je budete dodirnuli.

162
00:19:39,618 --> 00:19:41,734
Jer sve prethodno poznavanje 
predmeta

163
00:19:41,938 --> 00:19:43,974
zasniva se na dodiru, ne na vidu.

164
00:19:44,258 --> 00:19:46,488
Sada vise niste slepi.

165
00:19:46,738 --> 00:19:48,012
Moj posao je

166
00:19:48,058 --> 00:19:49,173
da vam pomognem

167
00:19:49,218 --> 00:19:50,412
kako da koristite vase oci...

168
00:19:50,458 --> 00:19:52,369
i da razumete ono sto vidite.

169
00:19:52,418 --> 00:19:54,693
Zapravo, ja nisam previse 
zabrinut za taj aspekt.

170
00:19:54,738 --> 00:19:57,047
Ono sto me brine je 
vase psihicko stanje.

171
00:19:57,658 --> 00:20:00,126
Nakon povratka vida...

172
00:20:00,338 --> 00:20:02,374
vecina pacijenata imaju imaju 
osecaj otudjenosti i straha.

173
00:20:02,418 --> 00:20:03,328
Dr. Lo,

174
00:20:03,378 --> 00:20:05,687
da li drugi Dr Lo a neki rod?

175
00:20:06,098 --> 00:20:07,611
Da li mislite na Dr C.T. Lo?

176
00:20:07,658 --> 00:20:09,853
Da, on mi je ujak.

177
00:20:10,898 --> 00:20:13,856
Nego... ukoliko ste sati danas
zavrsili sa poslom?

178
00:20:17,058 --> 00:20:19,697
Ms Wong mi je poslednji 
pacijent za danas.

179
00:20:20,018 --> 00:20:22,930
U redu... nego vidite, moram uhvatiti
let danas

180
00:20:23,218 --> 00:20:26,176
Mogu li vas zamoliti da otpratite 
Mun do kuce posle ovoga?

181
00:20:27,858 --> 00:20:29,496
Vidim , naravno.

182
00:20:29,538 --> 00:20:31,051
Nakon svega, pocev od danas...

183
00:20:31,098 --> 00:20:33,134
Moam izvoditi Ms Wong napolje
da je obucavam.

184
00:20:33,298 --> 00:20:34,128
OK

185
00:20:34,178 --> 00:20:36,294
Mozete ici sada.

186
00:20:36,538 --> 00:20:37,971
Meni odgovara.

187
00:20:38,018 --> 00:20:41,727
Navikla sam se.

188
00:20:49,458 --> 00:20:52,530
Ovo ste vi kao mala devojcica.

189
00:20:52,778 --> 00:20:55,338
Ovo je vas otac snimio
pre mnogo godina...

190
00:20:55,618 --> 00:20:59,293
tako da bi mogli videti ovo
ako vam se povrati vid.

191
00:20:59,978 --> 00:21:03,368
Stao je sa snimanjem
kada se razveo od vase majke.

192
00:21:03,418 --> 00:21:05,807
Ovo je bilo pre 7,8 godina.

193
00:21:06,058 --> 00:21:07,457
Bako...

194
00:21:07,498 --> 00:21:08,851
Jel istina kad se tata vratio,

195
00:21:08,898 --> 00:21:11,093
da nas je vodio u Vankuver?

196
00:21:11,138 --> 00:21:13,368
Znam da nisi htela da ides,

197
00:21:13,578 --> 00:21:17,173
ali zivot u  Vankuveru bi isao 
sporijim tempom.

198
00:21:17,378 --> 00:21:19,255
To bi bilo odlicno za tebe.

199
00:21:19,298 --> 00:21:21,937
Ja ne znam ni kineski da citam
kako bi naucila Engleski?

200
00:21:22,738 --> 00:21:24,217
Bako,

201
00:21:24,258 --> 00:21:26,249
Ne zelim da se oslanjam
na nekoga zauvek.

202
00:21:26,298 --> 00:21:27,936
Zelim da naucim da pisem

203
00:21:27,978 --> 00:21:29,889
i nadjem posao u Hong Kongu.

204
00:21:29,938 --> 00:21:31,451
Zelim biti nezavisna.

205
00:21:31,498 --> 00:21:35,173
Tvoj otac ce se brinuti kada 
budes odlazila na posao.

206
00:21:36,498 --> 00:21:39,376
Moram da operem sudove
Ostavicu te da gledas sama.

207
00:22:25,258 --> 00:22:26,691
Mogu li ti pomoci?

208
00:22:26,738 --> 00:22:30,253
Da li si videla moj izvestaj kartice?

209
00:22:30,458 --> 00:22:32,096
Ne.

210
00:22:32,138 --> 00:22:33,491
Da li vasi zive ovde?

211
00:22:33,538 --> 00:22:36,416
Mun, ko je to?

212
00:22:36,458 --> 00:22:38,289
To je mali decak, bako.

213
00:22:38,338 --> 00:22:40,693
Da nije kartiza pala na 
nasu terasu?

214
00:22:43,898 --> 00:22:45,695
Taj klinac ti dosadjuje.

215
00:22:45,738 --> 00:22:48,855
Samo ga ignorisi.

216
00:24:08,018 --> 00:24:10,532
Klinac, sta jedes to?

217
00:24:12,098 --> 00:24:15,613
IMnogo sam gladan.

218
00:24:18,858 --> 00:24:21,088
Koji je tvoj problem?

219
00:25:17,538 --> 00:25:20,371
Slusajte svi ,imamo dve dobre 
vesti danas.

220
00:25:20,618 --> 00:25:23,416
Prva...

221
00:25:23,458 --> 00:25:28,691
Ms Tone Deaf je imala uspesnu
operaciju!

222
00:25:32,218 --> 00:25:35,608
I druga, za nas Bozicni
dobrotvorni koncert...

223
00:25:35,778 --> 00:25:39,532
Nastupace Vanessa Mae!

224
00:26:07,698 --> 00:26:10,974
Mr. Cheng zasto ja nisam dobila 
prakticni raspored?

225
00:26:17,258 --> 00:26:18,930
Mun, znas, posle svega...

226
00:26:18,978 --> 00:26:21,094
mi smo organizacija za slepe.

227
00:26:21,138 --> 00:26:23,732
Uvek si dobrodosla da vezbas
sa nama...

228
00:26:23,938 --> 00:26:26,611
ali mozda trba da uradite nesto 
drugo za predstavu,

229
00:26:26,858 --> 00:26:27,847
