230
00:26:27,898 --> 00:26:29,331
ili brigu o nasim clanovima.

231
00:26:29,378 --> 00:26:30,652
Cak mogu da organizujem

232
00:26:30,698 --> 00:26:32,973
kako da pomognete centru.

233
00:26:33,498 --> 00:26:35,216
Mr. Cheng,

234
00:26:35,258 --> 00:26:37,488
Stvarno zelim da imam udela
u ovoj predstavi.

235
00:26:37,938 --> 00:26:39,053
Toliko dugo sam vezbala

236
00:26:39,098 --> 00:26:41,487
za ovaj koncert!

237
